{"tid":2403451,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"支持港國安法的羅兵咸點解有員工確診武肺","createTime":"2021-02-11T05:54:48.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-11T05:59:08.000Z","uid":26770,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"8f367fd527b34cb2b90a6f292da14d7432e7d501","tid":2403451,"uid":26770,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-11T05:54:48.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://paper.wenweipo.com/2020/07/03/FS2007030005.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fpaper.wenweipo.com%2F2020%2F07%2F03%2FFS2007030005.htm&d=i0%2FHWd2N8RLCa1A1b4xPLHO0ZW31AiaZ%2BXmqixBX3cM%3D&h=4dbf6879\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://paper.wenweipo.com/2020/07/03/FS2007030005.htm</a><br />\n<strong>曾獲文匯報班反人類畜牲點名稱讚</strong><br />\n<br />\n香港文匯報訊（記者 岑健樂）美國宣布撤銷香港特殊待遇，市場關注香港的國際金融中心地位會否因而動搖。羅兵咸永道香港企業客戶主管合夥人<span class=\"violet\">黃煒邦</span>昨於記者會表示，香港國安法並無影響香港國際金融中心及上市集資的地位，因過去一年不論香港發生了什麼變化，有興趣赴港上市的公司沒有明顯減少的跡象，而現時約有170間公司正在本港申請上市，與去年同期相若。<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a1dce8f2a169eb48812189e48320fa55e9803d96","tid":2403451,"uid":26770,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-11T05:59:08.000Z","msg":"狗共借防疫為名強制檢測建立納粹基因庫<br />\n但大家都睇到感染率都偏低<br />\n<br />\n點解PwC會中呢<br />\n係咪車公造美<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hd.stheadline.com/news/daily/fin/789941/%E6%97%A5%E5%A0%B1-%E8%B2%A1%E7%B6%93-%E5%89%B5%E7%A7%91%E8%88%87%E6%8A%95%E8%B3%87-%E7%A7%91%E6%8A%80%E5%9C%92%E7%BE%85%E5%85%B5%E5%92%B8%E5%90%88%E4%BD%9C-%E6%94%9C%E6%89%8B%E6%8E%A8%E5%8B%95%E5%89%B5%E7%A7%91%E7%A4%BE%E7%BE%A4\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhd.stheadline.com%2Fnews%2Fdaily%2Ffin%2F789941%2F%25E6%2597%25A5%25E5%25A0%25B1-%25E8%25B2%25A1%25E7%25B6%2593-%25E5%2589%25B5%25E7%